{"tid":2393751,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港已經完撚咗，只不過係你地圍爐取暖未瞓醒先至感覺唔到～","createTime":"2021-02-03T16:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T04:47:28.000Z","uid":219007,"like":35,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"179582c778d4950751663376122d27c92659a896","tid":2393751,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"出邊香港人唔會唔知道有問題存在，佢哋當然唔會忘記2019既事，但係會唔會麻木又係另一件事。  「周梓樂係慘，但係都要生活㗎，算啦吞左佢啦」，「多一件事不如少一件」 呢啲就係香港人嘅係閪格，到今日都冇變過。佢哋嘅麻木速度係其他其他地方嘅人快幾倍，所以面對嚟緊嘅通識改革，SIM卡實名制等，自然就唔識嬲。 <br />\n<br />\n香港成個社會嘅所有人底裏各自已經有晒選擇盤算，留底既基本上佢已經預咗接受（即係頭先所講嗰啲麻木者），而決定移民嘅亦都唔會理香港往後例如通識改革嘅事，因為佢都預咗走唔需要再理。 而剩返嗰啲就係去到今日仲不停叫反抗嘅人，即係連登仔同部份大學生。<br />\n<br />\n我可以同你地講，你哋唔會頂得好耐。  當成個社會都將你哋呢種意識形態嘅人排除出外嘅時候，留低嘅人自然就會為咗搵飯食而決定鵪鶉，大學生長大後都係會咁。呢一樣野係非常之現實一定要面對，冇人能夠為咗骨氣完全完全唔使食飯，除非你有後著。<br />\n<br />\n香港已經完咗，只不過係因為完咗幾個月你班友仔仲喺度嘈先唔覺得係咩事。  唔同階層嘅人都會因為要明哲保身而選擇割蓆，就連所有大學都將你哋全面吞噬，唔使357年，出面社會嘅人見到你自然會彈開，客觀就係孤立，仲要反抗嘅人只會無立足之地，仲要不斷承受牢獄之災，呢個就係你哋嘅下場，難聽到要咁講。<br />\n<br />\n仲話要抗爭嘅人講到底，其實只不過係你條氣唔撚信。 但係如果一個人每次都為啖氣而做嘢，結果一定奶野。 所以做之前一定要諗清楚，承受得起結果先好做。 <br />\n<br />\n香港嘅光芒就係2019年綻放左一下，熄咗之後香港人回復正常，但係其實底裏各自已經有晒決定，一方面繼續做既得利益者踐踏其他人，一方面又有啲賺埋最後一筆走頭，又有啲繼續麻醉自己做隻豬，而最快死先既就會係話要反抗嘅人。所以依家要做嘅就係各自為自己前途着想，要為自己好，唔好諗埋啲on9野。<br />\n<br />\n香港人嘅性格係好撚閪，係你地太後生未明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04a3f1a6e7408557a2dc4a82527d75874e6b1f6","tid":2393751,"uid":219007,"like":9,"dislike":8,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gcFbAoG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgcFbAoG.gif&h=6059721f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efcaf141fc3c332d82856e869de71f6cb6655af8","tid":2393751,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:44:46.000Z","msg":"Do you own due diligence, thank you <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fdcc9c09166c4b7fa013073806c2c1e08d2d25f","tid":2393751,"uid":114193,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"連下sir 唔係話唔好理香港變成點嘅咩？<br />\n做乜仲出咁多新聞post? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後作為連下sir 信徒<br />\n幫手推廣下佢嘅概念<br />\n俾連登班黑暴知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ef4b06a90798dcc85c8f60302887b67300c7446c","tid":2393751,"uid":300918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efcaf141fc3c332d82856e869de71f6cb6655af8","tid":2393751,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:44:46.000Z","msg":"Do you own due diligence, thank you <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"I agree with you<br />\ndon't compete with your fellows<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414114cdf2f89b06257f7e12b07c0314cd7fa883","tid":2393751,"uid":70878,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"三條路<br />\n移民<br />\n順民<br />\n暴民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f73d6b13fb7a29d1e1843432be5cbfa6eca33bf","tid":2393751,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"講經咩 我以為你有入黨路數先入黎睇PO咋"},{"pid":"136617bd95f17ee1e428083c5fb4ab1f154b8be0","tid":2393751,"uid":108016,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"唔出去抗爭<br />\n唔代表一定要投共"},{"pid":"77a346d82be8537a9309817ad90471d4be4167c8","tid":2393751,"uid":66618,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e04a3f1a6e7408557a2dc4a82527d75874e6b1f6","tid":2393751,"uid":219007,"like":9,"dislike":8,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gcFbAoG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgcFbAoG.gif&h=6059721f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T21:32:57.000Z","msg":"9upper 啤梨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c98227d397ea8e55f73de01d915a1bc4f11116","tid":2393751,"uid":60145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T22:04:30.000Z","msg":"1997已經完左<br />\n呢廿幾年都係自欺欺人"},{"pid":"4d2c93b91f1c245f91bee6aad0dd9a6d0a6c2e03","tid":2393751,"uid":90692,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T22:14:26.000Z","msg":"唔覺得呢啲叫閪，仲叫人抗爭就真係閪啦。"},{"pid":"568710bc781e95fe47c78d31e0c42d293182992a","tid":2393751,"uid":246823,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T22:20:19.000Z","msg":"當香港人係自己人, 連登仔係自己人之中既自己人<br />\n我作為IT人, 軟件台既網友更加係連登仔之中既自己人<br />\n<br />\n但話比自己人知想整個新language, 換黎既係群起既攻擊, 奚落, 恥笑, 負皮 (多謝比正皮既幾位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n想整個新language<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gCNDrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gCNDrS</a><br />\n<br />\n呢刻我真係好撚憎呢d香港人, 認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131d3798df8489c06e4ef8c8edfc740355c1082c","tid":2393751,"uid":389613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T22:20:49.000Z","msg":"著名放負五毛 <span class=\"red\">連下四城</span> (aka 狗眼看人妻、香港旗飄楊)<br />\n<br />\n如果見到有通街都知係五毛/PR嘅狗隻<br />\n#228回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rcLiBsX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rcLiBsX</a><br />\n<br />\n扮自己人，重要時刻就開新 thread 刻意放負，矮化族群，打擊抗爭意志，毀滅港人自信及互信：<br />\n<br />\n［挑機］香港人咁樣食飯，其實呢個孽自己有份作，無得怪人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2130525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2130525</a><br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n<br />\n由 2019 年已經開始不停叫人散水，放棄：<br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2329311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2329311</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2323506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2323506</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2315353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2315353</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2276817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2276817</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184746</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2073990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2073990</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2046361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2046361</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850160</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768364</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681018</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548844</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417635</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383029</a><br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n<br />\n除左我講過，仲有其它用戶有講過：<br />\n唔該admin正視下「連下四城」呢個會員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2007585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2007585</a><br />\n<br />\n黃世澤都開名屌9你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GoXnMWAMWQc?t=1316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGoXnMWAMWQc%3Ft%3D1316&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=0e76487c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GoXnMWAMWQc?t=1316</a><br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n<br />\n另外以下為連下四城分身：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvJpRW3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvJpRW3.png&h=0950adb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ig1bwW3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fig1bwW3.png&h=f7f8a3fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTJk9JK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTJk9JK.png&h=ddbb159a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n<br />\n樓主我屌你全家阿，死藍蛆 <br />\n<br />\n選擇大量題材不斷洗白自己既戶口，但到左重要時刻就會現身分化，主要利用文章暗示做 False <br />\nImpression，通過人碎片化去閱讀既習慣，通過 highlight 同總結，將文章 highlight <br />\n部分帶出概念投射左入腦，刻意標籤矮化定性某D行為，消磨抗爭意志及陣營團結，惡毒到不得了"},{"pid":"0a289a385010885bc6b1377c2750ae39e3fbb746","tid":2393751,"uid":62259,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T22:26:57.000Z","msg":"唔解釋咁多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxBuoYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxBuoYz.jpg&h=fcdf4414&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09b5a5a7c0ba92c631621120a269faf5bfd930ac","tid":2393751,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"568710bc781e95fe47c78d31e0c42d293182992a","tid":2393751,"uid":246823,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T22:20:19.000Z","msg":"當香港人係自己人, 連登仔係自己人之中既自己人<br />\n我作為IT人, 軟件台既網友更加係連登仔之中既自己人<br />\n<br />\n但話比自己人知想整個新language, 換黎既係群起既攻擊, 奚落, 恥笑, 負皮 (多謝比正皮既幾位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\